Spiderbait are considered Australia's rock royalty with over half a million albums sold, 5 Top 20 albums, 19 ARIA Nominations and 2 ARIA awards!
They were the first band to make it to the #1 spot on Triple J hottest 100 for their pulsating guitar anthem 'Buy Me A Pony' and their cover of 'Black Betty' scored them a number 1 single on the ARIA chart and a Top 20 single in the US.
After an 8 years recording hiatus they are back with a new self-titled album produced by François Tetaz. The album remains true to their rock heritage mixed with sweet sounds, double kick and gritty ball-busting riffs.
